<DATELINE>
   DUBLIN
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
SOME Pounds 20m in government finance for the Laganbank property development
project in Belfast was approved yesterday, giving the go-ahead to Ewart, the
project's lead developer, to begin contracting for an estimated Pounds 110m
in construction work.
Mr Barry Gilligan, managing director of the Belfast-based company said:
