FT  09 DEC 92 / UK Company News: Mansfield Brewery up to Pounds 6.7m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
MANSFIELD Brewery, the Yorkshire and east Midlands brewer, lifted pre-tax
profits from Pounds Pounds 6.36m to Pounds 6.67m in the 26 weeks to
September 26.
Group turnover edged ahead to Pounds 60.8m (Pounds 59m). Mr Joss Nangle,
