costs' resulted in trading profits up 13 per cent at Pounds 6.65m. This was
struck after a Pounds 900,000 provision for bad and doubtful debts in the
free trade.
Earnings per share inched up to 28.8p (28.4p) and the interim dividend is
lifted 10 per cent to 4.4p (4p).
